<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Github Data Display</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/2.7.3/Chart.bundle.js" integrity="sha256-o8aByMEvaNTcBsw94EfRLbBrJBI+c3mjna/j4LrfyJ8=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="jumbotron vertical-center">
      <div class="col-10" style="margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col col-4">
                  <h1>Prefered Irish Programming Languages</h1>
                  <p>
                    Based on a query of some 1000 Irish Github Users, displayed in the following interface
                    is a representation of the favourite Irish programming languages. The data was attained
                    by attaining the 1000 Irish users from a Github API call. The URL of each users repository
                    was subsequently attained. Each repository was analysed and the amount of bytes of code in
                    each language was attained. Having this data, a representation of the most used languages
                    and the amount of bytes of each language can be generated.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="col col-8">
                  <canvas id="myChart" width="400" height="175"></canvas>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ZMP7rVo3mIykV+2+9J3UJ46jBk0WLaUAdn689aCwoqbBJiSnjAK/l8WvCWPIPm49" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-ChfqqxuZUCnJSK3+MXmPNIyE6ZbWh2IMqE241rYiqJxyMiZ6OW/JmZQ5stwEULTy" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="./script/home.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
